### 5. Obtener todas las cuentas
GET {{baseUrl}}/bank-accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Obtener estadísticas
GET {{baseUrl}}/bank-accounts/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Obtener cuenta por ID (reemplazar :id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/bank-accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Actualizar cuenta (reemplazar :id)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bank-accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountHolderName": "Juan Carlos Pérez García"
}

### 9. Eliminar cuenta (reemplazar :id)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/bank-accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

